# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Real files (hashed assets, the /demo app, /downloads/* binaries) are served first by Pages.
# Anything else falls through to index.html so client-side routes like /downloads, /releases,
# and /changelog resolve on a direct load or refresh. The explicit /demo rule keeps the demo
# app's own index.html in charge of its subtree.

/demo/*    /demo/index.html   200
/*         /index.html        200
